{"name":"The Woman from the Woods - equipment1","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","translations":{"es":{"name":"La Dama de los Bosques - equipo1","system":{"description":"<p>Una muñeca y un soldadito de madera, los únicos objetos que llevaba conmigo cuando me encontraron. No sé de dónde vienen, pero los guardo como un tesoro</p>"}}},"contentKey":"equipment1.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","sequence":1,"ownerName":"The Woman from the Woods","ownerNameEs":"La Dama de los Bosques"}},"system":{"description":"A doll and a little wooden soldier — the only items I had with me when I was found. A worn-out gray travel dress stained with blood. A sharp butcher’s knife. A hair ribbon, gift from a Hunter of the Order. A cookbook filled with recipes for cakes and sweets","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
